\begin_layout Subsection*
Distant Dreams
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
At its heart, 
\series bold
Luminous: the Dream
\series default
 is about the contrast between dreams and idealism vs the harshness of realities
 and the necessities of survival.
 A Luminous may dream of a better world, that they know may one day be true.
 She may defeat the monster on her own.
 Maybe even she could be elected, help guide the city council towards reform.
 She can rescue the boy she loves.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
But even with their shining magic, they may only do so much on their own.
 They can only win when a hundred million small victories one day add up
 into something greater.
 Even as they are closer than ever before, their dreams always seems a distant
 future, still trapped faraway behind the veil of sleep.
\end_layout

