Distant Dreams
\begin_inset Quotes xrd
\end_inset

 is the title of Luminous.
 
\begin_inset Quotes xld
\end_inset

A Storytelling Game of Distant Dreams
\begin_inset Quotes xrd
\end_inset

.
 So is 
\begin_inset Quotes xld
