 means a lot of different things, and that is intentional.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Does 
\begin_inset Quotes xld
\end_inset

Distant Dreams
\begin_inset Quotes xrd
\end_inset

 mean how far from reality a dream is – the way the Luminous are not all
