 interweaving all of humanity together into a single tapestry.
 The strength of the connection between two given people is called Intimacy.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
Connected:
\series default
 The two people are so close that the distinction between them does not
 matter, often being bound by magical vows and ties.
 This usually applies to extremely close lovers, platonic life partners,
 and those bound by vows such as those between a Changeling and the Avowed
 or the 
